videos.headline: Mississippi State fumbles on opening drive to set up LSU TD
videos.description: Kayshon Boutte catches an 11-yard TD for LSU following Malik Heath's fumble for Mississippi State.

videos.headline: Cordale Flott makes leaping interception for LSU
videos.description: Cordale Flott forces Mississippi State's second turnover of the day.

videos.headline: Mississippi State QB completes pass to himself
videos.description: Mississippi State quarterback Will Rogers' pass goes off an LSU player's helmet and back to himself for a loss of four yards.

videos.headline: Boutte reels in 64-yard TD catch for LSU
videos.description: Kayshon Boutte scores his second touchdown of the game to give LSU a 14-3 lead over Mississippi State.

videos.headline: Trey Palmer walks in a 58-yard TD for LSU
videos.description: Max Johnson finds a wide open Trey Palmer who takes it into the end zone for LSU's third TD.

videos.headline: Will Rogers hits Makai Polk in stride for Mississippi State TD
videos.description: Mississippi State gets on the board thanks to a 29-yard TD pass from Will Rogers to Makai Polk.

videos.headline: Two Mississippi State defenders collide leading to a 41-yard LSU TD
videos.description: TE Kole Taylor escapes the Mississippi State defense for LSU's fourth touchdown of the game.
